<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ح وك:</span> <span class="c2">(حَاكَ)</span> الثَّوْبَ نَسَجَهُ وَبَابُهُ قَالَ وَ <span class="c2">(حِيَاكَةً)</span> أَيْضًا فَهُوَ <span class="c2">(حَائِكٌ)</span> وَقَوْمٌ <span class="c2">(حَاكَةٌ)</span> <span class="c2">(حَوَكَةٌ)</span> أَيْضًا بِفَتْحِ الْوَاوِ وَنِسْوَةٌ <span class="c2">(حَوَائِكُ)</span> وَالْمَوْضِعُ <span class="c2">(مَحَاكَةٌ)</span> .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>